---
import ArticleLayout from '../../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
import { localizedPath } from '../../i18n/utils';

const locale = 'en';
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="Contact WorthCalc"
  description="Reach the WorthCalc team about calculator bugs, math corrections, feature requests, or partnership inquiries."
  locale={locale}
  updated="2026-07-03"
>
  <p>
    WorthCalc is a small, independently run site, so we keep contact simple:
    email us directly rather than filling out a form.
  </p>
  <p>
    Email: <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    Good reasons to write in:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>You think a calculator's math is wrong — tell us the inputs you used and what result you expected, and we will check it.</li>
    <li>A default value (like a membership fee or interest rate) looks out of date.</li>
    <li>You have an idea for a new "is it worth it" calculator.</li>
    <li>You found a bug, broken link, or display issue on mobile or desktop.</li>
    <li>You're interested in advertising or a partnership.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We read every message, though as a small team we can't guarantee a
    response to every one. For general questions about how the site works,
    see the <a href={localizedPath(locale, '/about')}>About page</a>, and for
    how we handle data, see our
    <a href={localizedPath(locale, '/privacy')}>Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>
</ArticleLayout>
